---
import BaseLayout from '~/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Donate"
  description="Support Spark & Anvil's mission to keep 138 educational iOS apps free for every kid, forever. We're a non-profit (501(c)(3) status pending; donations via our fiscal sponsor are tax-deductible)."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-16 pb-8">
    <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 mb-4 bg-forge text-warm text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider rounded-full">Non-profit (pending)</span>
    <h1 class="font-brand font-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl text-anvil dark:text-warm mb-4">
      Keep the apps free, forever.
    </h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-anvil/70 dark:text-warm/70 leading-relaxed">
      Spark &amp; Anvil makes 138 educational iOS apps for kids ages 5-14 — all free, no ads, no
      in-app purchases, no tracking. We can keep it that way because we're restructuring as a
      mission-driven non-profit.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Donor tiers (stub) -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-8">
    <h2 class="font-brand font-bold text-2xl text-anvil dark:text-warm mb-6">Recurring monthly</h2>
    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
      {[
        { amount: '$5', label: 'Friend', desc: 'A tank of coffee for the maker.' },
        { amount: '$10', label: 'Supporter', desc: 'One app\'s hosting + analytics for a month.' },
        { amount: '$25', label: 'Sustainer', desc: 'A character art commission for the cast.' },
        { amount: '$100', label: 'Builder', desc: 'One classroom\'s worth of curriculum kits.' },
      ].map(tier => (
        <article class="bg-white dark:bg-anvil/40 rounded-2xl p-5 border-2 border-anvil/15 dark:border-warm/15 hover:border-forge transition-colors">
          <div class="text-3xl font-brand font-bold text-forge mb-1">{tier.amount}<span class="text-sm text-anvil/60 dark:text-warm/60">/mo</span></div>
          <div class="font-brand font-bold text-anvil dark:text-warm mb-2">{tier.label}</div>
          <p class="text-sm text-anvil/70 dark:text-warm/70 leading-snug">{tier.desc}</p>
        </article>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Teacher Network Sustainers tier (cross-referenced from /teach Option C) -->
  <section id="teacher-network-sustainers" class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-8">
    <div class="bg-forge/10 dark:bg-forge-light/10 border-2 border-forge/30 dark:border-forge-light/30 rounded-2xl p-6">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4 flex-wrap">
        <div class="flex-1 min-w-[260px]">
          <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-forge dark:text-forge-light font-bold mb-1">Special program tier</div>
          <h2 class="font-brand font-bold text-2xl text-anvil dark:text-warm mb-3">Teacher Network Sustainers</h2>
          <p class="text-anvil/80 dark:text-warm/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Sustain the platform that lets teachers keep <strong>100%</strong> of their class fees. Our
            <a href="/teach" class="underline hover:text-forge">teacher network</a> charges teachers
            <strong>nothing</strong> — no commission, no platform fee. The ~$50K-$140K/yr operating cost
            is covered by donors like you + foundation grants. Your monthly gift directly funds
            background-check coverage, ForgeClassroom infrastructure, COPPA compliance, and parent-side
            discovery for live small-group classes ages 9-14.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-anvil/60 dark:text-warm/60">
            Tax-deductible via fiscal sponsor while IRS Form 1023 determination clears. Optional public
            recognition on this page (we'll never publish your name without consent).
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-right">
          <div class="text-3xl font-brand font-bold text-forge mb-1">$25-$100<span class="text-base text-anvil/60 dark:text-warm/60">/mo</span></div>
          <div class="text-xs text-anvil/60 dark:text-warm/60 mb-3">suggested range</div>
          <a href="mailto:hello@spark-and-anvil.com?subject=Teacher%20Network%20Sustainer%20signup" class="btn-primary">
            Join the tier →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- One-time + founder circle (stub) -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-8">
    <h2 class="font-brand font-bold text-2xl text-anvil dark:text-warm mb-6">One-time + founder circle</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <article class="bg-white dark:bg-anvil/40 rounded-2xl p-5 border-2 border-anvil/15 dark:border-warm/15">
        <div class="text-3xl font-brand font-bold text-forge mb-1">$1,000</div>
        <div class="font-brand font-bold text-anvil dark:text-warm mb-2">One-time</div>
        <p class="text-sm text-anvil/70 dark:text-warm/70 leading-snug">
          Funds a full app's question-kit refresh wave (16 kits × 25 questions) + the AI-mentor
          persona finalization for that app.
        </p>
      </article>
      <article class="bg-forge text-warm rounded-2xl p-5">
        <div class="text-3xl font-brand font-bold mb-1">$10,000+</div>
        <div class="font-brand font-bold mb-2">Founder Circle</div>
        <p class="text-sm text-warm/90 leading-snug">
          Direct line to the founder, board observer seat (optional), recognition on
          /impact, custom acknowledgment in next annual report.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Donate CTA (stub) -->
  <section class="bg-anvil/5 dark:bg-warm/5 py-12">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <p class="text-anvil/80 dark:text-warm/80 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
        <strong>Donation flow coming soon.</strong> We're finalizing fiscal sponsorship (Hack
        Foundation expected) to make donations immediately tax-deductible while our IRS Form 1023
        determination clears (~12-18 months from filing). In the meantime, email
        <a href="mailto:hello@spark-and-anvil.com" class="underline hover:text-forge">hello@spark-and-anvil.com</a>
        to be the first to know.
      </p>
      <a href="mailto:hello@spark-and-anvil.com?subject=Spark%20%26%20Anvil%20donation%20interest" class="btn-primary">
        Email us about donating →
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Tax + transparency -->
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    <h2 class="font-brand font-bold text-2xl text-anvil dark:text-warm mb-4">Tax deductibility &amp; transparency</h2>
    <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-anvil/80 dark:text-warm/80 leading-relaxed">
      <li>
        <strong>501(c)(3) status:</strong> pending. We've filed (or are filing) IRS Form 1023.
        Typical determination period is ~191 days median, 12-18 months real-world.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Fiscal sponsorship bridge:</strong> while 1023 clears, donations route through
        our fiscal sponsor (Hack Foundation / HCB or similar). Sponsor's EIN provides
        tax-deductibility today.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Annual report:</strong> we'll publish a public annual report covering revenue,
        expenses, kids reached, partners, board, and 2026 audit findings.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>No ads, no tracking, no sale of data:</strong> these don't change under
        non-profit status; they're load-bearing to the mission.
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
